scripts.build-closure: npm run build && google-closure-compiler --warning_level=VERBOSE --jscomp_off=globalThis --jscomp_off=checkTypes --externs utils/build/externs.js --language_in=ECMASCRIPT5_STRICT --js build/three.js --js_output_file build/three.min.js
scripts.dev-test: concurrently --names "ROLLUP,ROLLUPTEST,HTTP" -c "bgBlue.bold,bgRed.bold,bgGreen.bold" "rollup -c utils/build/rollup.config.js -w -m inline" "npm run dev --prefix test" "http-server -p 8080"
scripts.lint-examples: eslint examples/jsm --ext js --ext ts --ignore-pattern libs && tsc -p utils/build/tsconfig-examples.lint.json
scripts.lint-fix: eslint src --ext js --ext ts --fix && eslint examples/js/ --ext js --ext ts --ignore-pattern libs --fix
scripts.test: npm run test-lint && npm run test-unit
scripts.test-lint: eslint src --ext js --ext ts && tsc -p utils/build/tsconfig.lint.json
